<i> under the screen name</i>
<i> "Victor Surge"</i>

29:58.923 --> 30:00.923
<i> as part</i>
<i> of a Photoshop contest</i>

30:00.966 --> 30:02.216
<i> to try to create something</i>

30:02.259 --> 30:04.218
<i> that looked real</i>
<i> that really wasn't.</i>

