36:45.162 --> 36:50.165
with what I would call
universal human struggles

36:50.208 --> 36:52.250
that we continue
to have today.

36:52.294 --> 36:54.169
I think that's
one of the reasons

36:54.212 --> 36:57.881
why people are
responding to this tale,

36:57.925 --> 36:59.507
and they're telling
