39:44.591 --> 39:47.926
We don't know
whether he's evil or good.

39:47.969 --> 39:51.304
We don't know
whether he's going to do
anything to these children.

39:51.348 --> 39:53.223
The children never return.

39:53.266 --> 39:55.058
<i>Nobody ever hears about them.</i>

39:55.102 --> 39:58.645
(ominous music playing)

40:04.111 --> 40:06.027
<i> But the Pied Piper</i>
<i> does live on.</i>

40:35.559 --> 40:36.933
♪ ♪

40:45.110 --> 40:46.192
(Casey speaks)

40:50.782 --> 40:52.407
(Morgan speaks)

40:55.078 --> 40:56.411
Umm...

41:00.959 --> 41:03.418
<i> (car driving)</i>

41:03.461 --> 41:05.461
<i> (Angie sighs)</i>

41:05.505 --> 41:08.715
<i> It's almost like</i>
<i> she was living a whole</i>
<i> nother life inside her head</i>

41:08.758 --> 41:12.302
that we just--
that we just didn't know about.

41:19.394 --> 41:22.437
It's hard with kids because...

41:22.480 --> 41:25.815
they don't necessarily
know how to differentiate

41:25.859 --> 41:29.235
between fantasy
and reality to begin with.

41:30.655 --> 41:32.614
So, it's just hard to know...

41:32.657 --> 41:34.657
where-- where to draw the line.

41:34.701 --> 41:36.451
Where does that become...

41:37.996 --> 41:39.120
abnormal?

41:41.791 --> 41:43.082
So even though, you know,

41:43.126 --> 41:45.585
looking back,
maybe there were some signs.

41:47.339 --> 41:49.297
It's everything in retrospect.

41:59.809 --> 42:03.811
It's been two months
to the day on the calendar

42:03.855 --> 42:08.816
that she's been
in Washington County
Juvenile Detention Center.

42:09.986 --> 42:11.236
The first day was rough.

42:11.279 --> 42:12.487
You know, you get in there...

42:14.366 --> 42:17.951
you have to learn
all your check-in procedures
and everything.

42:20.413 --> 42:23.456
You know, you get back there,
and you don't know
what to expect.

42:23.500 --> 42:26.751
There's you,
there's a pane of glass
with metal bars behind it,

42:26.795 --> 42:29.629
and then...
there's our daughter.

42:29.673 --> 42:31.172
That's how it works.

42:35.512 --> 42:37.470
(Trussoni speaks)

42:37.514 --> 42:39.013
(Anissa speaks)

