(heavy metal music playing)

44:23.328 --> 44:26.120
(music stops)
Man: My voice is
going to take you

44:26.164 --> 44:29.082
to a very calm
and peaceful place.

44:29.125 --> 44:33.336
♪ ♪
(distortion, static)

44:33.380 --> 44:34.879
Man:
So this part,

44:34.923 --> 44:38.132
striking into
any soft tissue
in the body--

44:38.176 --> 44:40.301
the eyes, the cheeks,

