♪ Dog goes woof,
cat goes meow,
bird goes-- ♪

44:59.197 --> 45:02.031
Ah! Why do you
stick a baby

45:02.075 --> 45:05.535
in the blender
feet first?

45:05.578 --> 45:08.413
(demonic voice) So you can see
the expression on it's face.

45:08.456 --> 45:10.832
