<i> (Trussoni speaks)</i>

1:00:17.740 --> 1:00:19.114
<i>(Anissa speaks)</i>

1:00:28.792 --> 1:00:30.250
<i> (Trussoni speaks)</i>

1:00:30.294 --> 1:00:31.793
<i>(Anissa speaks)</i>

1:00:47.353 --> 1:00:51.063
After playing
on the playground
equipment for a while,

1:00:51.106 --> 1:00:54.983
they went into the bathroom,
all three of them.

1:00:55.027 --> 1:00:56.485
<i> (Casey speaks</i>
<i> on video)</i>

1:00:57.488 --> 1:00:59.780
<i>(Morgan speaks)</i>

1:01:01.325 --> 1:01:02.449
<i> (Casey speaks)</i>

1:01:11.502 --> 1:01:14.294
<i>(Anissa speaking</i>
<i>on video)</i>

1:01:20.636 --> 1:01:22.761
♪ ♪

