She didn't want
to go to sleep,

1:01:48.539 --> 1:01:51.164
so she didn't sit there
with her eyes closed,

1:01:51.208 --> 1:01:55.710
and at some point,
Anissa hit the front
of her head

1:01:55.754 --> 1:01:58.463
and caused the back
of her head to...

1:01:59.383 --> 1:02:00.674
slam against the wall.

1:02:12.187 --> 1:02:13.228
Basically.

1:02:24.116 --> 1:02:25.157
<i>(Anissa speaks)</i>

1:02:31.373 --> 1:02:35.709
And Morgan said,
"I thought we agreed that
you were going to do this."

1:02:36.712 --> 1:02:38.462
Attorney:
Did Payton tell you anything

1:02:38.505 --> 1:02:40.881
